dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents zoning for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Zoning_2015.gdb. [Rural zoning districts for townships that fall under Waupaca County Zoning. Zoning data is tax parcel based.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. Best available date of this dataset is 5/12/2015. For online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.waupaca.wi.us/landinformation/Data.aspx.
